Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:09.79,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.79,0:00:20.16,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.35,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.80,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.80,0:00:53.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.55,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:07.02,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.02,0:01:14.33,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:21.03,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.03,0:01:28.26,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.56,0:01:36.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to move on to\Nthe next phase of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:43.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't lose face in the high council.\NChor Tempest can't go on as it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:57.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Until the repairs on the Arcus Prima\Nare completed, Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:02:03.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,...will board the Messis and be\Ncharged with border reconnaissance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:06.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? We're boarding that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:11.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't be unreasonable. You should\Njust be thankful Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:15.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's right.\NThat old boat should do just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:18.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't mind at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:34.30,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Birds in a Cage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:04.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, are we really\Ngonna live here, all together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:09.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe, you'd better save your\Ncomplaining till you've secured a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:12.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,The beds on the window side\Nare first come, first served.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:14.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Best regards, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:24.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Best regards, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:35.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister, do you think we'll\Nbe living here for a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just like we can't\Nchange what's happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.52,0:03:41.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,...there's no telling\Nwhat's in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,You may be right about that, Kaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:58.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun, where's Mamina?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:00.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:09.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,We believe the damage\Nwas caused in transit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:13.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,The communication-wire\Nejectors have come a bit loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:15.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can you manage\Nwithout replacing parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:17.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:21.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,There'll be a severe shortage of\Nreplacement parts. Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:26.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're having\Na hard time, Waporif.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:30.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not compared to\Nyou sibyllae. You're all so noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:33.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everything must seem new to you...\NI'm sure you're taken aback.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:39.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Noble you say? We can't afford\Nto worry about being noble right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:43.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,As long as you can\Nfly a Simoun, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:45.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:57.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then that's how I'd like\Nthe reconnaissance tasks divided.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:02.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Very well.\NBut if I may, Sibylla Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:03.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:09.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is the finest chor and\Nthe pride of Simulacrum Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:14.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Though my crew and I are\Ngreatly honored by your presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:17.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,...why were you assigned\Nto an old front-line vessel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:21.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain, the inconvenience\Nis written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,N-No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter. You're quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:32.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,And someone from a different chain\Nof command is invading your bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:35.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Very well, Sibylla Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:38.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I will refrain from\Nasking you anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla, please stop... Sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's beneath you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:55.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I've worked in\Nkitchens since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:59.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I really enjoy doing this, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:47.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,This area along the Shoukoku border\Nis most vulnerable to invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,This may be a scheduled recon\Nflight, but don't drop your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:53.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Scheduled recon flight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:55.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:57.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,When Simoun sibyllae take to the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:59.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,...she is "praying to the skies."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:03.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Controlling a Simoun is\N"speaking with a Simoun."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:08.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, we took off to speak with\Nour Simouns and pray to the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:10.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:15.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're to be back at base at noon.\NTill then, don't forget to be vigilant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:21.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a mouse! A mouse, a mouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:24.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:27.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean there are mice on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:33.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aren't you scared, Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:37.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I grew up on a farm,\Nso there were lots of mice around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:40.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, the same goes\Nfor you. Right, Mamina?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:48.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Two o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,So far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's the third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:56.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,They can really get\Non your nerves, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:59.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, let's head back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:02.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, they're too far away to pursue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,It'd be wiser to return\Nand make our report.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:24.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't stand living in a room like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:29.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why does Dominüra get\Nher own room? It's definitely fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:33.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was thanks to Dominüra's pleading\Nthat we were able to board this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:36.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,You really shouldn't say such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of hearing your\Nwhining and complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:47.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aer...\NIs it true that mice bite people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:48.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:50.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,So they do bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:51.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Welcome back. So?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:31.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,We spotted far off what we\Nbelieved to be enemy planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:34.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,When they noticed us,\Nthey fled immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:35.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:38.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:41.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,They were so far\Nwe lost them in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,You should report to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:46.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, the acting captain is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:51.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've explained my position.\NWould you like to hear it again, Kaim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:56.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest's regina is Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:10:00.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra is the mediator\Nbetween our chor and Wauf...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the patrol ship Messis's captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:04.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Chor Tempest comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:07.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta,\Nmake your report to Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:11.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everybody! Lunch is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:15.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I heard Mamina made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:35.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,You seem sad, Guragief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:41.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth,\NI'm feeling very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:46.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,However, Anubituf, I was sure\Nthat you'd be feeling the same way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:48.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:53.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest,\Nthose glorious Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:56.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we're the ones\Nwho took away that glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:00.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what it takes, I'll save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:05.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I shall do everything in my\Npower to summon them back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:13.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is it really in their best interests to be\Ncalled back to the Arcus Prima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even I can't answer that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:20.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:22.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:23.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:24.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Smells great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:26.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:27.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's making me all warm inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:33.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,It tastes great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:38.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's still plenty,\Nso you can have seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:42.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina, aren't you eating too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:05.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:10.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened the other day... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:15.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's pretend the whole thing never\Nhappened. Is that clear, Mamina?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:20.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey,\Nwhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:26.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're so mean.\NYou could at least tell us, Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:29.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can I sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:48.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, Mamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:51.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk to you\Nafter lunch if you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:52.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,The new sibylla made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:03.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:25.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're pretty late for someone\Nwho called me here, Roatreamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:27.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I got lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:30.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,On a puny boat like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:32.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind.\NWhat did you want to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,So what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you don't say anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:45.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:02.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come now, Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:08.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not that I didn't\Nhave any feelings for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:13.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can I patch things up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:18.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Patch things up? That sounds\Nlike we were actually friends before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:23.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Till the end, one of us will always\Nbe above and the other below.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:24.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:28.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just what were\Nyou thinking that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,That I wanted to be friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:34.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I feel the same way even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:37.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,This conversation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:43.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was always envious\Nof those braids of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,But these are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:49.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,You plait your hair because\Nyour parents told you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:55.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,But those things don't mean\Na thing to a child. To me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:57.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they were a rich girl's hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:10.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:21.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is the chor all Simoun\Nsibyllae worship and take pride in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:24.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the finest chor of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,On behalf of all Simoun sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:30.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I beg you to consider\Npreserving Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:35.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you mean\NChor Tempest as sibyllae?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:39.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or Chor Tempest as\Na squadron of warriors?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:45.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,You say you want us to preserve\NChor Tempest, but which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Twelve sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:51.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,...who become each other's pairs\Nand draw Ri Majons across the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:55.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is only one Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:01.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were there that day\Nas well, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:05.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I heard everything that\Nwent on during that hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:11.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Vura and Onasia, Chor\NTempest was saved from disbanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:14.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was also due to your\Nbrilliant speech, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:22.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am not looking to blame\Nanyone for this war we're waging.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:27.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter how tragic and painful it\Nis now, I believe it was meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:31.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether or not that is\NTempus Spatium's will...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:34.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it makes no difference to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:38.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I no longer even care whether\Nit's God's will anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:44.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,However, I do have\None question for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:49.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Despite all this, can I still\Ncall myself a Simoun sibylla?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:52.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you overheard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:01.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, I'd like you to select\Nthe next sibyllae to go on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:06.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, next will be two pairs,\Nyou and Rimone, Alty and Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:08.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:10.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:16.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,The truth is you're the one\Nwho saved Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:20.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,You negotiated with the council\Nto keep us, provided we be sent...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:23.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to the front lines\Non this ship, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:24.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:28.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is the greatest\Nchor in Simulacrum Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:30.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is no doubt about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:34.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still, how can you do such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's pretty neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:14.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a keepsake from my grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:18.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:21.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Something's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:26.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to tell me the enemy's\Nbehavior in this morning's patrol again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fine... But what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:33.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I recall, you sighted distant traces\Nof the enemy several times...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:36.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and they immediately fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,We encountered them\Nthree times to be precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you getting at, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:45.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you four\Nreally saw them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:51.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then they spotted us first and\Nrevealed themselves on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Most likely. Paraietta, we must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:56.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll notify the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:19:00.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,The rest of you,\Nhurry to the flight deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:03.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Neviril.\NIt never occurred to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:06.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your scouting flight\Npath has been tracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:10.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra and the others are being\Nambushed. We're at the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:14.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're at the front lines\Nof the enemy's assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:20.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina and\NRoatreamon aren't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:21.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:25.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm the auriga.\NKaim, please pair with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:27.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:30.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Yun, you're my sagitta.\N— Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Get a move on, Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Waporif.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:38.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll send Mamina and Roatreamon\Nas soon as they arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:53.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,What will you do,\NSibylla Roatreamon, Sibylla Mamina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,The others have already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:56.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina, let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:20:01.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,No! I'm not going to pair\Nwith you! Didn't I tell you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:05.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Over my dead body.\NIt's never going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:23.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,W-What... What do you\Nthink you're doing, Roatre?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:26.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,You called me that\Nwhen we were little too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:32.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Roatreamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:37.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone's in danger...\NThey could all die...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:44.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is no time for us\Nto be hesitating, Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:03.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Roatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:06.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Emergency positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:14.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:29.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're still sniveling?\NWe're on our way to meet the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:31.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not it... That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:35.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just that I've always,\Nalways worn braids...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:38.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:51.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now's our chance!\NWe can take on that many.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:52.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Iron Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:13.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,That meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:16.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:20.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was the mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:47.87,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.87,0:22:52.11,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:59.15,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.15,0:23:06.81,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.59,0:23:19.67,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.67,0:23:24.84,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:28.85,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.85,0:23:32.82,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:38.72,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:44.27,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:47.70,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:53.37,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.37,0:23:59.89,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:06.63,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.63,0:24:11.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's our job as sibyllae\Nto take the soldiers near that town.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.92,0:24:16.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.79,0:24:18.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,United Front.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:19.97,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}United Front
